author: Amai Ta. Yume
text:
As usual! Thank you for the stream. This after stream was shocking. I was playing Genshin Impact when I tried to look at these and thought, "wow I am a bit late". After the disaster last stream.

But watching towards the panicking Rushia and the careful Rushia, oh how much you have grown by hours.  Digging endless to find more diamonds and discover magma blocks along the way. You are indeed so lovable and great! I love you so much. I don't if this feelings is admiration, but I am proud to watch you here!

Hope you had a great night. Sleep tight Rushia, take care as usual. Thank you fellow members and Rushia's fans for the heartwarming support on her and the super chats you'd given. They indeed cheer her up.

She didn't need to say and translate to us global fans but she did anyways! Rushia no matter what, we won't turn on you. I will always be here watching and hopefully be a member as well when the time comes for me with the right job.

This stream was so late, it was already early in the morning, but I have not regret such a thing and not breath out a sigh. Every precious moment counts 🥰🥰

author: Nexcell Pride
text:
A great encore with good ending for a tragedy at previous stream, despite the non programmed transmission (Or in another words, guerrilla stream)

Finally Rushia-hime went for another adventure full of dangers, due to water filtrations, floods and lava filtrations.
Additionally, Rushia look so calm at start, respect to the sad ending at previous stream... She needed to be serene, and the night peak was a great moment to make the changes... Or much better, upgrade everything...

And again at Supacha Yomi Time, more love given to her via LiveChat. :_ハート: :_きゅん:

Finally the after ending was shown like as she usually gets. :_ちょうちょ:
